                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13114396" author="nehanarkhede" created="Sun, 25 Sep 2011 23:33:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch corrects the queue.poll logic to respect the queue timeout. Before this, under very low traffic, the producer ended up waiting for a timeout proportional to number of events added to the queue, the upper bound being the batch size. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13114783" author="junrao" created="Mon, 26 Sep 2011 16:55:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13116040" author="junrao" created="Wed, 28 Sep 2011 00:52:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Neha. Just committed this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
